doc.cdescr: I WAS  DRIVING DOWN THE ROAD ONE DAY IN MY CAR AND THE THEFT SYSTEM  LIGHT STAYED ON  THEN  STARTED  BLINKING  FOR  A  COUPLE  OF  DAYS THEN  ONE  DAY  THE CAR WOULDN'T START AND THE THEFT LIGHT JUST STAYED  ON  IN I TOOK IT TO A DEALER IN THEY SAID IT WAS A THEFT SYSTEM MALFUNCTION AND THAT MANY 2001 MALIBU'S HAVE THE SAME PROBLEM AND  THAT IT WOULD COST $300.00 TO 400.00 TO BE FIXED. *JB
